Class Field

java.lang.Object
  ast.ASTNode
      ast.Member
          ast.Field

public class Field
extends Member

The Field class represents a field (instance variable) declaration appearing in a class declaration. It contains a variable type (type), a name (name), and an optional initialization expression (init).
